{
  "page": "Mountains of the Morn",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">Not to be confused with the <a href=\"/index.php/Mountains_of_the_Moon\" title=\"Mountains of the Moon\">Mountains of the Moon</a>.</div>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:WorldofIceandFire.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Mountains of the Morn is located in The Known World\"><img alt=\"Mountains of the Morn is located in The Known World\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/10/WorldofIceandFire.png/300px-WorldofIceandFire.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/10/WorldofIceandFire.png/450px-WorldofIceandFire.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/10/WorldofIceandFire.png/600px-WorldofIceandFire.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 66.7%; left: 93.1%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -4px; top: -4px; width: 8px; font-size: 8px; z-index:100;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/8px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Mountains of the Morn\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/12px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/16px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size:&#160;%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: -6.5em; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\">Mountains of the Morn</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\">The <a href=\"/index.php/Known_world\" title=\"Known world\">known world</a> and the location of the Mountains of the Morn\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>The <b>Mountains of the Morn</b> are a mountain range in the <a href=\"/index.php/Further_East\" title=\"Further East\">Further East</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Geography\">Geography</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mountains_of_the_Morn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Geography\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The Mountains of the Morn run roughly in a north-to-southeast curve. Northwest of the mountains are the <a href=\"/index.php/Five_Forts\" title=\"Five Forts\">Five Forts</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Bleeding_Sea\" title=\"Bleeding Sea\">Bleeding Sea</a>, while to the northeast are the <a href=\"/index.php/Dry_Deep\" title=\"Dry Deep\">Dry Deep</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Cities_of_the_Bloodless_Men\" title=\"Cities of the Bloodless Men\">Cities of the Bloodless Men</a>. The <a href=\"/index.php/Hidden_Sea\" title=\"Hidden Sea\">Hidden Sea</a> and its two cities, the <a href=\"/index.php/City_of_the_Winged_Men\" title=\"City of the Winged Men\">City of the Winged Men</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Carcosa\" title=\"Carcosa\">Carcosa</a>, are located in the southeastern stretch of the mountains. West of the Mountains of the Morn is <a href=\"/index.php/Yi_Ti\" title=\"Yi Ti\">Yi Ti</a>, while to the south are the <a href=\"/index.php/Shadow_Lands\" title=\"Shadow Lands\">Shadow Lands</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiafthe_known_world.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiafthe_known_world.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> The <a href=\"/index.php/Ash_(river)\" title=\"Ash (river)\">Ash</a> runs from the Mountains of the Morn to the <a href=\"/index.php/Jade_Sea\" title=\"Jade Sea\">Jade Sea</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond:_asshai-by-the-shadow.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond:_asshai-by-the-shadow.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Culture\">Culture</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mountains_of_the_Morn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Culture\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The Mountains of the Morn are considered legendary by Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Yandel\" title=\"Yandel\">Yandel</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond:_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond:_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mountains_of_the_Morn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtloiafthe_known_world.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtloiafthe_known_world.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i>, The Known World.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond:_asshai-by-the-shadow.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond:_asshai-by-the-shadow.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Bones and Beyond: Asshai-by-the-Shadow.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond:_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond:_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Bones and Beyond: Yi Ti.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404144920\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.052 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.084 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 800/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 12400/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4654/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 2139/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 13/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1777/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.020/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 4.51 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   70.843      1 -total\n 58.88%   41.713      1 Template:Hatnote\n 21.87%   15.493      1 Template:Location_map\n 20.31%   14.391      1 Template:Location_map+\n 14.41%   10.212      3 Template:Ref\n 13.89%    9.843      1 Template:Location_map~\n  9.12%    6.459      3 Template:Ref/core\n  6.27%    4.443     22 Template:Location_map_Known_World\n  4.13%    2.928      1 Template:References\n  1.87%    1.322      3 Template:Location_map/decdeg\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:14378-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404144920 and revisi